commit_message: Fixed ordering of parameters in README and dir_kallisto_map_fastq.sh. Changed name of merged .tsv file
Maps all fastq file pairs in a directory to the indexed genome
Changed accession path to be consistent with others

Init commit. Scripts for RNA-seq mapping. Further automation can be obtained easily by combining scripts. NOTE: In current state, directory structure must be set up prior to using scripts. (Oct. 2, 2018)
